ngdoing when his clients are cleared its because ehrengraf has committed misdeeds up to and including murder to exonerate his client and often frame another for the crimes the first short story featuring ehrengraf “the ehrengraf defense” was published in ellery queen’s mystery magazine in  by  twelve stories had been published and in  block completed an eleventh story “the ehrengraf settlement” all eleven were collected and published in an evolume ehrengraf for the defense  in addition to writing the scripts for a handful of television episodes over the years—including in  two episodes of the espn series tilt—block cowrote the screenplay for my blueberry nights a  film directed by wong karwai and starring norah jones selected bibliographyedit matthew scudder novelsedit the sins of the fathers  time to murder and create  in the midst of death  a stab in the dark  eight million ways to die  when the sacred ginmill closes  out on the cutting edge  a ticket to the boneyard  a dance at the slaughterhouse  a walk among the tombstones  the devil knows youre dead  a long line of dead men  even the wicked  everybody dies  hope to die  all the flowers are dying  a drop of the hard stuff  the night and the music  a collection of matthew scudder short stories and novelettes  in total bernie rhodenbarr novelsedit burglars cant be choosers  the burglar in the closet  the burglar who liked to quote kipling  the burglar who studied spinoza  the burglar who painted like mondrian  the burglar who traded ted williams  the burglar who thought he was bogart  the burglar in the library  the burglar in the rye  the burglar on the prowl  the burglar who counted the spoons  there are also three bernie rhodenbarr short stories like a thief in the night cosmopolitan may  the burglar who dropped in on elvis playboy april  and the burglar who smelled smoke mary higgins clark mystery magazine summerfall  these stories are collected in the  anthology enough rope evan tanner novelsedit the thief w