ications  high school sex club nightstand books  college for sinners corinth publications  sexpot nightstand books  the twisted ones nightstand books   lust corinth publications  reissued as cinderella sims by greenleaf classics gutter girl bedstand books  lover nightstand books  reissued as gigolo johnny wells sin devil nightstand books  four lives at the crossroads  written as don hollidayedit circle of sinners   in collaboration with hal dresner border lust  reissued by hard case crime as borderline written as lesley evansedit strange are the ways of love  written as lee duncanedit fidel castro assassinated  reissued by hard case crime as killing castro written as anne campbell clarkedit passport to peril  written as ben christopheredit strange embrace   originally written as a tiein to johnny midnight tv series in collaboration with donald e westlakeedit a girl called honey midwood books  credited to sheldon lord and alan marshall so willing midwood books  credited to sheldon lord and alan marshall sin hellcat nightstand books  credited to andrew shaw other fictionedit strange are the ways of love  as lesley evans reissued in  as shadows by jill emerson babe in the woods   block ghostwrote this novel following the death of author william ard only ard is credited death pulls a doublecross  reissued as cowards kiss mona  reissued as sweet slow death and by hard case crime as grifters game markham  reissued as you could call it murder  written and published as a tiein to markham tv series the girl with the long green heart  deadly honeymoon  after the first death  the specialists  ronald rabbit is a dirty old man  ariel  code of arms  into the night   block completed this novel from a manuscript by cornell woolrich random walk  small town  the girl with the deep blue eyes  short storiesedit some days you get the bear collected stories  enough rope collected stories  one night stands and lost weekends  dollys trash and treasures written for audio presentation in the